                                text="&lt;p>&lt;span class=&quot;light-font&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-32-reg&quot;>Learn how Eyoel Tsegay's work across the health care ecosystem can make a difference for patients.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;"
